WEBVTT

01:37.660 --> 01:40.530
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.259 --> 01:43.670
[Episode 4]

01:44.229 --> 01:46.350
So, you're all cultivators

01:46.590 --> 01:48.200
from Lingji Mountain?

01:49.200 --> 01:51.070
I am Lin Muhan,

01:51.200 --> 01:53.200
the Young Sect Master of Lingji Mountain.

01:53.200 --> 01:54.800
And this is my junior sister,

01:55.070 --> 01:55.600
Jiang Ji.

02:00.120 --> 02:01.510
I am Jin Lun, an unaffiliated cultivator.

02:01.510 --> 02:02.200
And the one outside

02:02.200 --> 02:03.680
who wields music as a weapon

02:03.680 --> 02:06.480
is Nangong Guhong
from the Solar and Lunar Cavern.

02:11.310 --> 02:12.310
It's not very polite

02:12.310 --> 02:14.030
to ask a young lady her name

02:14.590 --> 02:16.000
so abruptly, you know.

02:17.840 --> 02:19.280
This immortal lady is Zuo Yingying

02:19.280 --> 02:21.410
of the Cyan-Rainbow Sect of Beixiang.

02:22.079 --> 02:24.280
Well then, with all you immortals here,

02:24.520 --> 02:26.870
I feel much more at ease.

02:27.240 --> 02:28.030
Could you please take
that cultivator away

02:28.030 --> 02:29.680
as soon as possible?

02:29.800 --> 02:30.329
That way,

02:30.630 --> 02:32.690
I won't have to live in constant fear.

02:32.800 --> 02:34.060
Rest assured, My Lord.

02:34.240 --> 02:35.240
That goes without saying.

02:35.240 --> 02:35.770
Alright.

02:35.840 --> 02:37.300
Then let's set off at once.

02:37.470 --> 02:38.400
No rush, no rush.

02:38.680 --> 02:40.190
Please, My Lord, don't be hasty.

02:40.190 --> 02:41.590
We've been traveling all this way

02:41.590 --> 02:42.960
and should take some time
to rest and recover.

02:42.960 --> 02:44.030
How about this, My Lord—

02:44.030 --> 02:44.630
you find

02:44.800 --> 02:45.630
a guest room

02:45.630 --> 02:46.760
and rest well first.

02:47.079 --> 02:48.630
After we've had something
to eat and drink,

02:48.630 --> 02:49.960
we'll set out together.

02:50.150 --> 02:50.880
Fair enough.

02:51.079 --> 02:52.680
I was way too hasty—

02:52.840 --> 02:54.140
how could I have overlooked that?

02:54.140 --> 02:54.800
Attendant!

02:55.030 --> 02:55.520
Hurry

02:55.750 --> 02:56.750
and clean this up.

02:56.840 --> 02:58.700
Bring out your best food and wine—

02:58.840 --> 02:59.710
I'll pay.

03:00.400 --> 03:02.190
You all enjoy yourselves first.

03:02.190 --> 03:03.790
I really can't go on anymore—

03:03.870 --> 03:05.430
I'll go rest in my room.

03:06.150 --> 03:07.150
Quick, let's go.

03:07.150 --> 03:08.000
Help me to my rest—

03:08.000 --> 03:08.800
hurry, hurry!

03:10.190 --> 03:11.850
A wise man knows when to yield.

03:12.030 --> 03:13.360
We're no match for them.

03:38.680 --> 03:41.520
Sir, you are such a handsome young man.

03:41.960 --> 03:43.490
Why not have a drink with me?

03:44.430 --> 03:46.150
My friend here can't hold his liquor.

03:46.150 --> 03:47.120
If you want to drink,

03:47.120 --> 03:48.980
I'll keep you company, Immortal.

03:49.470 --> 03:51.130
But I'm not interested in you.

03:56.520 --> 03:58.190
I'm a straightforward person,

03:58.190 --> 03:58.870
and I can't stand

03:58.870 --> 04:00.680
faithless men hurting devoted women.

04:00.680 --> 04:02.000
That Landlady from earlier—

04:02.000 --> 04:03.530
she knows you, doesn't she?

04:03.710 --> 04:04.960
She got beaten,

04:05.240 --> 04:07.500
and you didn't lift a finger to help—why?

04:13.590 --> 04:15.150
Strong build,

04:15.430 --> 04:17.040
steady breath…

04:17.870 --> 04:19.329
you're a skilled fighter.

04:20.079 --> 04:21.010
Here's the deal—

04:21.620 --> 04:22.600
go stab that

04:22.600 --> 04:24.000
little wretch Jiang Ji,

04:24.750 --> 04:26.310
and I'll protect you.

04:26.510 --> 04:27.310
You won't die.

04:34.190 --> 04:35.600
What a blockhead.

04:38.870 --> 04:40.070
The food is poisoned!

05:17.950 --> 05:19.630
How do you like
the Immortal-Sealing Powder

05:19.630 --> 05:21.600
from Chongling Valley?

05:40.430 --> 05:41.560
This is all a misunderstanding.

05:41.560 --> 05:42.270
Everyone, put down your weapons

05:42.270 --> 05:43.480
and let's talk this through.

05:43.480 --> 05:45.000
You serve the authorities—

05:45.000 --> 05:46.260
why are you against us?

06:25.630 --> 06:26.750
A mortal body…

06:27.720 --> 06:29.320
yet you withstood my strike.

06:30.310 --> 06:30.950
Young man,

06:31.950 --> 06:33.310
you're quite impressive.

06:33.310 --> 06:34.720
The fact that he could take
that strike from you

06:34.720 --> 06:37.070
suggests his cultivation
has already reached a transcendent level.

06:37.070 --> 06:38.390
The divide between immortals and mortals

06:38.390 --> 06:39.920
is no mere figure of speech—

06:40.000 --> 06:40.920
one word apart,

06:40.920 --> 06:42.120
yet worlds apart.

06:42.870 --> 06:43.870
Still, young man,

06:44.360 --> 06:46.000
let me give you a piece of advice:

06:46.000 --> 06:47.430
before you try to show off next time,

06:47.430 --> 06:48.390
make sure

06:48.390 --> 06:49.430
you know your own limits.

06:49.430 --> 06:51.290
Not every immortal sect disciple

06:51.750 --> 06:53.210
is as reasonable as we are.

06:54.920 --> 06:55.580
Never mind.

06:55.870 --> 06:57.390
It was just a misunderstanding.

06:57.390 --> 06:59.120
Take this bottle of Yangyuan Pills

06:59.120 --> 07:00.070
as an apology.

07:01.870 --> 07:03.870
Yangyuan Pills are valuable stuff—

07:03.920 --> 07:05.450
they can both heal injuries

07:05.560 --> 07:07.360
and enhance one's cultivation.

07:07.360 --> 07:08.070
Landlady,

07:08.360 --> 07:09.890
you really hit the jackpot.

07:10.830 --> 07:11.630
Enchantress,

07:11.870 --> 07:13.510
you're no good either.

07:16.390 --> 07:17.800
I didn't misjudge you—

07:18.430 --> 07:19.690
you've got some skill.

07:20.040 --> 07:21.160
I'll let it slide this time.

07:21.160 --> 07:22.190
Next time we meet,

07:22.360 --> 07:24.490
show me what you're really capable of.

07:31.490 --> 07:32.090
Looks like

07:32.430 --> 07:35.290
a trip to Chongling Valley
will have to wait for now.

08:06.060 --> 08:08.590
[Xin Xie Manor]

08:11.680 --> 08:12.190
Who is it?

08:12.190 --> 08:12.920
Who's there?

08:13.070 --> 08:13.560
Who—

08:17.510 --> 08:18.070
Sheng,

08:18.510 --> 08:20.360
you wretched disciple—
what are you doing?

08:20.360 --> 08:22.000
Put me down immediately!

08:23.510 --> 08:24.510
Stop struggling.

08:24.750 --> 08:26.000
Your cultivation is too advanced—

08:26.000 --> 08:27.160
you were afraid you wouldn't get drunk,

08:27.160 --> 08:28.240
so you sealed your own major acupoints

08:28.240 --> 08:29.920
with the Nine-Element Technique.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.800
For 7 days,

08:31.000 --> 08:32.870
you won't be able to use
a trace of your powers.

08:32.870 --> 08:34.070
You won't break free.

08:35.000 --> 08:36.360
The court's dispatch—

08:36.510 --> 08:37.549
you left it in the wine cellar

08:37.549 --> 08:38.510
for 4 whole days.

08:38.840 --> 08:40.120
I only found it today.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.840
The letter says a female cultivator
surnamed Xin

08:42.840 --> 08:43.860
caused trouble in the capital,

08:43.860 --> 08:46.260
slaying 3 officials to avenge her husband.

08:46.270 --> 08:48.150
The court is inviting disciples
from all major immortal sects

08:48.150 --> 08:49.520
to capture the female cultivator.

08:49.520 --> 08:52.080
What does the court
have to do with you anyway?

08:52.200 --> 08:52.960
Our Xin Xie Manor

08:52.960 --> 08:54.030
has lived in seclusion for years—

08:54.030 --> 08:56.030
we've long had no contact with them.

08:56.130 --> 08:57.120
You wretched disciple,

08:57.120 --> 08:58.630
put me down now!

08:59.390 --> 09:00.750
Listen to me carefully.

09:01.120 --> 09:03.120
A female cultivator, surnamed Xin—

09:03.150 --> 09:05.530
beautiful, kind-hearted,
always standing up for the weak.

09:05.530 --> 09:06.000
Doesn't that

09:06.000 --> 09:07.630
sound exactly like my senior sister?

09:07.630 --> 09:08.910
Beautiful and kind-hearted?

09:08.910 --> 09:10.440
Is that really what the letter says?

09:10.440 --> 09:11.100
Out with it—

09:11.270 --> 09:12.410
what exactly did you

09:12.510 --> 09:14.790
send my senior sister
down the mountain to do?

09:14.790 --> 09:16.030
If that's really what it says,

09:16.030 --> 09:17.240
it does sound like Xin.

09:17.240 --> 09:17.800
But…

09:17.910 --> 09:19.870
she shouldn't be going to the capital.

09:19.870 --> 09:21.870
Where did you send my senior sister?

09:22.790 --> 09:24.750
She insisted on going herself.

09:24.750 --> 09:26.790
She said she was heading back
to the countryside to visit her auntie—

09:26.790 --> 09:29.080
her auntie, already in her eighties
or nineties,

09:29.080 --> 09:30.080
didn't have much time left.

09:30.080 --> 09:31.150
She was determined to go,

09:31.150 --> 09:32.470
and I couldn't stop her.

09:32.470 --> 09:34.270
Then why did she go to the capital—

09:34.270 --> 09:35.870
and even avenge her husband?

09:36.000 --> 09:37.660
When did she even get married?

09:37.790 --> 09:39.360
Did you arrange a marriage for her again

09:39.360 --> 09:40.320
without her consent?

09:40.320 --> 09:41.390
I-I didn't do that.

09:41.390 --> 09:41.850
Well...

09:42.510 --> 09:44.000
it might not even be her.

09:44.000 --> 09:45.240
There are plenty of cultivators

09:45.240 --> 09:46.000
with the surname Xin out there—

09:46.000 --> 09:47.240
why must it be her?

09:48.320 --> 09:49.120
That won't do.

09:49.150 --> 09:50.280
I have to go find her.

09:51.390 --> 09:52.120
Sheng,

09:52.270 --> 09:54.200
you'll only make things worse if you go.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.390
You wretched disciple—

09:55.390 --> 09:57.240
put me down first!

09:57.360 --> 09:58.890
Whatever it is, we can talk it through.

09:58.890 --> 10:00.440
Sheng!

10:02.270 --> 10:04.320
Sheng!

10:09.190 --> 10:10.830
[Capital]

10:16.440 --> 10:17.870
[Liang Wenjing,
Minister of the Court of Judicial Review]

10:30.000 --> 10:31.370
[Mr. Gui, Qinghong Sect]

10:35.930 --> 10:37.440
Don't waste your energy.

10:38.510 --> 10:40.550
With me here today,

10:40.960 --> 10:43.150
you're not getting through that door.

10:44.360 --> 10:46.360
For a mortal to be born
with an immortal perception

10:46.360 --> 10:47.750
and step onto the path of cultivation—

10:47.750 --> 10:49.360
do you know how rare that is?

10:49.870 --> 10:51.730
And yet, despite having such a blessing,

10:51.730 --> 10:53.180
you fail to cherish it.

10:53.550 --> 10:55.880
Instead, you go against your moral sense,

10:55.910 --> 10:57.670
repeatedly breaking the rules

10:57.690 --> 11:00.180
and meddling in mortal affairs.

11:00.840 --> 11:03.670
Aren't you afraid
your cultivation will collapse

11:03.740 --> 11:05.500
and backfire on you?

11:05.960 --> 11:06.870
Enough talk—

11:07.200 --> 11:08.460
are we fighting or not?

11:10.840 --> 11:12.510
How utterly stubborn.

11:13.390 --> 11:15.920
Since you've wasted
such a rare opportunity,

11:15.960 --> 11:16.870
I might as well

11:17.510 --> 11:20.240
take you into my Sunblock Banner

11:20.240 --> 11:21.510
and refine you—

11:22.310 --> 11:25.430
at least that way you'll be of some use.

11:39.360 --> 11:40.320
How naive.

11:46.180 --> 11:47.980
Where do you think you're going?

13:04.200 --> 13:04.800
Oh no!

13:30.870 --> 13:31.600
I'm getting

13:32.430 --> 13:33.490
through this door.

13:39.510 --> 13:40.640
And the life inside—

13:41.320 --> 13:42.120
I'm taking it.

13:42.550 --> 13:43.810
You've got some nerve,

13:43.890 --> 13:45.800
daring to toy with me.

13:55.550 --> 13:57.360
Cutting off your own tail to survive—

13:57.360 --> 13:58.840
that takes nerve.

13:59.480 --> 14:00.720
It's been a long time

14:00.720 --> 14:02.510
since I've been pushed to this point.

14:02.510 --> 14:03.630
If that magic crow

14:03.790 --> 14:05.870
hadn't taken the blow for me,

14:06.030 --> 14:07.630
I might've fallen

14:07.630 --> 14:10.270
to a junior like you today.

14:11.360 --> 14:12.220
No need to rush.

14:12.600 --> 14:14.860
Sooner or later, you'll die all the same.

14:18.150 --> 14:19.680
Youth is a wonderful thing—

14:19.720 --> 14:21.390
your blood runs hot.

14:21.870 --> 14:23.320
With a blade in hand,

14:23.720 --> 14:25.910
it feels as if you could

14:26.240 --> 14:28.600
cut down all things under heaven
beneath your feet.

14:28.600 --> 14:30.000
But don't forget—

14:30.910 --> 14:33.320
everyone was young once.

14:33.910 --> 14:34.910
Cut the nonsense.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.270
What exactly are you trying to say?

14:37.270 --> 14:38.080
Very well.

14:38.630 --> 14:40.030
I will show you

14:40.030 --> 14:41.890
what real power looks like today.

14:59.960 --> 15:01.290
What formation is this?

15:02.200 --> 15:03.200
I haven't decided

15:03.720 --> 15:05.240
on a name yet.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.390
But you can call it—

15:07.840 --> 15:09.390
your burial ground.

15:39.080 --> 15:41.480
You can actually control
the power of time?

15:41.960 --> 15:45.030
Controlling time requires divine power—

15:46.000 --> 15:47.120
only gods

15:48.120 --> 15:49.630
can truly wield it.

15:50.200 --> 15:51.840
For cultivators like us,

15:52.150 --> 15:54.200
even if we devote our entire lives,

15:54.720 --> 15:57.120
we can only create a small realm.

15:57.630 --> 15:59.630
The extent of time reversal
we can achieve

15:59.630 --> 16:01.200
is no more than 50 years.

16:03.790 --> 16:05.580
But that is more than enough—

16:06.030 --> 16:06.840
to kill you.

16:11.720 --> 16:13.180
Such overwhelming power.

16:25.630 --> 16:27.120
This is when my cultivation

16:27.120 --> 16:28.870
is at its peak.

16:29.200 --> 16:31.400
Even against Golden Core cultivators,

16:31.910 --> 16:34.000
I would still have a chance to fight.

16:38.390 --> 16:40.750
With time reversed by 50 years,

16:41.360 --> 16:44.220
you're likely just a newcomer
to the immortal sect—

16:44.790 --> 16:46.670
probably haven't even crossed

16:46.670 --> 16:48.530
the threshold of Qi Cultivation.

16:51.120 --> 16:52.910
You can't defeat me.

16:53.320 --> 16:56.510
You'd be better off
surrendering obediently.

16:56.720 --> 16:59.360
I can grant you a swift death.

17:28.310 --> 17:29.550
You little girl…

17:30.240 --> 17:32.370
you really know how to provoke people.

17:36.160 --> 17:38.090
You ignorant fool courting death!

17:38.400 --> 17:39.480
Do you have any idea

17:40.350 --> 17:42.000
how much spiritual energy

17:42.440 --> 17:44.830
this formation consumes?

17:44.920 --> 17:47.200
How much essence blood
I have to sacrifice?

17:47.200 --> 17:49.010
You don't need to worry about that—

17:49.010 --> 17:49.540
because

17:50.240 --> 17:52.370
you won't be getting out of here alive.

18:00.640 --> 18:01.110
You...

18:02.030 --> 18:02.480
You...

18:03.000 --> 18:04.480
You asked why

18:04.480 --> 18:06.470
a mere Stage 4 Qi Refining cultivator
like me

18:06.470 --> 18:07.090
would dare

18:07.110 --> 18:09.070
to defy the world
and enter the mortal realm to kill,

18:09.070 --> 18:10.960
without fear of the immortal sects.

18:10.960 --> 18:12.310
Let me tell you now.

18:12.880 --> 18:14.010
I began cultivating

18:14.510 --> 18:16.240
under my master at the age of 12.

18:16.920 --> 18:19.720
Within a month, I had already grasped
the basics of Foundation Building.

18:19.720 --> 18:22.000
By 18, I had glimpsed
the threshold of the Golden Core.

18:22.000 --> 18:22.640
At 20,

18:23.110 --> 18:25.110
I reached the peak of my techniques.

18:35.110 --> 18:35.550
You…

18:36.200 --> 18:36.660
Golden…

18:37.440 --> 18:39.160
Golden Core cultivator?

18:45.680 --> 18:47.010
The stars are shifting—

18:47.440 --> 18:49.400
a practitioner is engaging
in a spell duel within the city.

18:49.400 --> 18:51.400
To be able to cause
such abnormal changes in the sky,

18:51.400 --> 18:53.550
they must be someone incredibly powerful.

18:53.550 --> 18:54.410
I didn't expect

18:54.550 --> 18:56.960
that in a place as wealthy and corrupt
as the capital,

18:56.960 --> 18:59.490
there are still hidden masters
lying in wait.

18:59.950 --> 19:01.370
♪ The vault of heaven is shaking,
on the verge of collapse ♪

19:00.000 --> 19:01.480
I was born with the Innate Dao Body

19:01.480 --> 19:02.480
and a pure immortal perception.

19:01.620 --> 19:04.490
♪ Yet I refuse to yield or make amends ♪

19:03.110 --> 19:05.000
I cultivated in the mountains
for 60 years

19:05.000 --> 19:06.620
and touched the Golden Core realm
3 separate times.

19:06.620 --> 19:08.050
♪ Rather than linger in fleeting winds
and moonlight ♪

19:06.680 --> 19:07.960
And yet I remain

19:07.960 --> 19:09.000
only a Stage 4 Qi Refining cultivator.

19:08.490 --> 19:12.300
♪ I would choose to stand
between all beings and fate itself ♪

19:09.240 --> 19:10.570
Why do you think that is?

19:11.160 --> 19:12.750
It's because I can't stand it.

19:12.750 --> 19:13.960
I can't stand this so-called

19:12.880 --> 19:15.910
♪ Walking the edge of a blade,
I cast aside life and death ♪

19:13.960 --> 19:15.160
justice of the world.

19:15.270 --> 19:16.720
I can't stand seeing
those struggling to survive

19:16.480 --> 19:20.000
♪ Vowing to speak out against injustice ♪

19:16.720 --> 19:18.050
being crushed by power.

19:18.310 --> 19:19.400
I can't stand watching the innocent

19:19.400 --> 19:20.490
wronged and killed.

19:20.490 --> 19:23.320
♪ If my cultivation turns
to ash and smoke ♪

19:20.910 --> 19:22.510
I've mastered great skills—

19:22.750 --> 19:23.960
I have the power
to move heaven and earth.

19:23.490 --> 19:25.360
♪ I still want to see this world ♪

19:25.310 --> 19:27.070
Yet because of this moral discipline,

19:25.420 --> 19:26.760
♪ Break into dawn once more ♪

19:26.790 --> 19:30.260
♪ Do you hear the raging tides of fury ♪

19:27.680 --> 19:29.070
I'm forced to turn a blind eye

19:29.070 --> 19:30.600
to the world's injustices.

19:30.750 --> 19:31.720
This?

19:31.120 --> 19:33.260
♪ How many sorrows
have finally been laid to rest ♪

19:32.350 --> 19:33.610
This is what I can't stand the most.

19:33.610 --> 19:36.420
♪ How many stand without bias or tilt ♪

19:36.450 --> 19:39.690
♪ Pointing to the sky,
questioning the moon ♪

19:39.710 --> 19:42.970
♪ I'd rather be a wandering immortal
in the mortal world ♪

19:43.240 --> 19:46.470
♪ And experience it all for myself ♪

19:46.610 --> 19:49.960
♪ Right and wrong, justice and evil ♪

19:50.020 --> 19:53.200
♪ In all the world,
I choose first the people ♪

19:53.810 --> 19:56.660
♪ How could the powerful lie drunk
in golden halls ♪

19:56.950 --> 19:59.950
♪ Illusions of heaven
and memory entwined ♪

20:00.290 --> 20:02.200
♪ I will still break
into this mortal realm ♪

20:00.630 --> 20:02.430
This is indeed a place of burial.

20:02.450 --> 20:04.450
♪ To demand a rightful ending ♪

20:03.350 --> 20:04.550
Too bad it's not mine—

20:04.660 --> 20:07.200
♪ Crossing the River of Heaven,
washing away right and wrong ♪

20:05.640 --> 20:06.640
it's yours.

20:07.980 --> 20:11.180
♪ For morality,
severing emotion and decay ♪

20:11.210 --> 20:13.830
♪ Only then can sun and moon
shine together ♪

20:14.760 --> 20:17.580
♪ Pointing to the sky,
questioning the moon ♪

20:18.160 --> 20:21.580
♪ I'd rather be a wandering immortal
in the mortal world ♪

20:21.600 --> 20:24.850
♪ Right and wrong, justice and evil ♪

20:25.090 --> 20:26.560
♪ I will still break
into this mortal realm ♪

20:26.580 --> 20:30.470
♪ To demand a rightful ending ♪

20:30.550 --> 20:33.360
♪ I strike the darkness
with a wild whip ♪

20:33.600 --> 20:38.130
♪ To save this world of mortal
fire and smoke ♪

20:43.350 --> 20:44.110
Do you think

20:44.310 --> 20:45.640
we've come too late?

20:47.480 --> 20:48.280
No, we haven't

20:49.640 --> 20:50.310
So certain?

20:51.350 --> 20:52.330
The way things looked last night

20:52.330 --> 20:53.510
was pretty intimidating.

20:53.510 --> 20:55.790
The other side definitely
isn't someone to be trifled with.

20:55.790 --> 20:57.720
Someone as slight as Immortal Xin—

20:57.880 --> 21:00.080
how could she possibly withstand that?

21:01.270 --> 21:03.030
The checkpoints haven't been withdrawn,

21:03.030 --> 21:03.680
and far more people are leaving the city

21:03.680 --> 21:04.880
than entering it.

21:05.240 --> 21:07.570
That means they still haven't caught her.

21:07.880 --> 21:08.610
Makes sense.

21:10.000 --> 21:11.500
Looks like Immortal Xin
won't be able to escape

21:11.500 --> 21:13.500
this "damsell in distress" moment.

21:17.270 --> 21:19.160
Come take a look!

21:19.160 --> 21:21.000
Little trinkets, small curios!

21:25.830 --> 21:27.200
The capital really is nice—

21:27.200 --> 21:27.800
so lively,

21:27.960 --> 21:29.560
it changes every single day.

21:30.200 --> 21:32.150
How long has it been
since you were last here?

21:32.150 --> 21:34.350
We haven't eaten for 3 days!

21:35.000 --> 21:35.880
Sir,

21:36.200 --> 21:37.110
please spare some change!

21:37.110 --> 21:39.160
We haven't had anything
to eat for 3 days and nights!

21:39.160 --> 21:40.480
Sir, please spare some change!

21:40.480 --> 21:41.000
Sir,

21:43.440 --> 21:44.590
please give us some money!

21:44.590 --> 21:45.650
Get lost, get lost.

21:45.880 --> 21:47.480
Please, just a little money.

21:48.920 --> 21:49.520
Thank you.

21:50.270 --> 21:52.640
Come to think of it,
this deal has really been bad luck.

21:52.640 --> 21:53.880
I went through so much trouble,

21:53.880 --> 21:54.880
all the way to Beixiang,

21:54.880 --> 21:55.350
and finally

21:55.350 --> 21:56.400
found his son—

21:56.640 --> 21:58.590
only to discover he was already dead.

21:58.590 --> 22:00.590
Now I even have to haul back a corpse.

22:01.240 --> 22:03.070
Can you help me find someone?

22:03.550 --> 22:05.200
My father's name is Lu Jingran.

22:05.200 --> 22:06.000
Got any money?

22:06.440 --> 22:06.960
Yes.

22:07.590 --> 22:08.240
But

22:08.510 --> 22:09.550
this is all I have.

22:10.070 --> 22:10.590
Still,

22:10.590 --> 22:11.880
I'll earn more in the future—

22:11.880 --> 22:13.160
whatever you want, I'll give it to you.

22:13.160 --> 22:14.160
Screw you!

22:14.720 --> 22:16.380
You think you can mess with me?

22:17.350 --> 22:17.920
San,

22:18.010 --> 22:18.640
look—

22:18.920 --> 22:20.310
it's a little freak.

22:21.350 --> 22:22.590
Indeed he is.

22:31.070 --> 22:31.920
Thank you, sir!

22:31.920 --> 22:33.160
Thank you, thank you!

22:33.480 --> 22:35.070
Thank you, sir—thank you!

22:35.510 --> 22:36.110
Thank you!

22:37.750 --> 22:39.080
The capital is this big…

22:39.160 --> 22:41.020
where are we supposed to find her?

22:44.880 --> 22:46.550
Candied hawthorn!

22:52.000 --> 22:53.510
Zuixian Restaurant...

22:57.070 --> 22:59.010
As the story goes, in last night's battle
at the Liang residence,

22:59.010 --> 23:00.340
the fight was so intense

23:00.350 --> 23:02.680
it blotted out the sky
and shook the earth.

23:02.920 --> 23:03.510
In the end,

23:03.510 --> 23:05.920
even Purple Spirit Lightning
was unleashed,

23:05.920 --> 23:08.240
causing abnormal celestial phenomena.

23:08.550 --> 23:09.480
The Liang family

23:09.480 --> 23:12.270
invited an immortal master from Beixiang
to oversee the situation.

23:12.270 --> 23:15.270
Rumor has it this Mr. Gui
possesses a magical artifact

23:15.550 --> 23:17.550
called the Sunblock Banner,

23:17.880 --> 23:19.310
with immense power—

23:19.750 --> 23:20.790
capable of instantly

23:20.790 --> 23:22.880
tearing a person apart.

23:23.160 --> 23:24.310
That's seriously impressive.

23:24.310 --> 23:26.510
If that Mr. Gui

23:26.510 --> 23:27.680
is as powerful as you say,

23:27.680 --> 23:28.790
then how could he

23:28.790 --> 23:30.350
possibly have died
by Immortal Xin's blade?

23:30.350 --> 23:31.110
Sir,

23:31.400 --> 23:33.790
don't rush to conclusions.

23:34.200 --> 23:36.750
Immortal Xin is now nowhere to be found—

23:36.830 --> 23:37.640
she might have

23:37.920 --> 23:40.640
already perished last night.

23:40.920 --> 23:42.310
If Immortal Xin is dead,

23:42.830 --> 23:44.240
then why would Lord Liang

23:44.240 --> 23:45.300
still be so afraid,

23:45.400 --> 23:46.590
inviting all the experts

23:46.590 --> 23:48.450
from the Great Xiangguang Temple

23:48.680 --> 23:51.080
to his residence
first thing this morning?

23:51.480 --> 23:52.510
Who on earth

23:52.590 --> 23:53.790
is this Immortal Xin?

23:54.200 --> 23:55.510
Which immortal mountain
does she come from?

23:55.510 --> 23:57.310
Why have we never heard of her before?

23:57.310 --> 23:59.510
As for which sect she comes from,
that's unknown.

23:59.510 --> 24:02.030
We only know she is Lord Lu's wife.

24:02.480 --> 24:03.220
Lord Lu?

24:03.830 --> 24:04.820
Which Lord Lu?

24:05.270 --> 24:07.750
Are we talking about Lord Lu Zhao
of the Royal Guards?

24:07.750 --> 24:09.240
He's the deputy county magistrate
of Wei County,

24:09.240 --> 24:10.040
named Lu Huai.

24:19.920 --> 24:20.980
Please have a seat,

24:21.310 --> 24:22.240
the dishes will be served shortly.

24:22.240 --> 24:22.770
Alright.

24:26.030 --> 24:28.230
They're talking about you downstairs.

24:28.310 --> 24:28.830
I know.

24:29.110 --> 24:29.830
Lu Huai?

24:30.400 --> 24:32.240
That name does sound unfamiliar.

24:32.240 --> 24:33.570
I've never heard of him.

24:34.070 --> 24:34.750
Lu Huai—Lord Lu.

24:34.750 --> 24:35.810
You don't know him?

24:36.070 --> 24:37.600
He was an upright official.

24:37.920 --> 24:39.440
Back when Wei County suffered a famine,

24:39.440 --> 24:40.770
he used clever strategy

24:40.960 --> 24:42.360
to save the people there.

24:43.030 --> 24:45.160
It's a pity the world
is blind and ignorant—

24:45.160 --> 24:46.590
deceived by treacherous men,

24:46.590 --> 24:47.990
unable to see his merits.

24:48.160 --> 24:49.440
In the end, he was falsely accused

24:49.440 --> 24:51.100
and put to a brutal execution.

24:52.350 --> 24:54.210
No wonder his wife was so furious—

24:54.270 --> 24:56.200
so she was seeking revenge for him.

24:56.240 --> 24:57.310
I heard the two of them

24:57.310 --> 24:58.970
were childhood sweethearts.

24:59.160 --> 25:00.360
Later, war broke out,

25:00.680 --> 25:02.880
and Immortal Xin
was taken into an immortal sect.

25:02.880 --> 25:04.440
Lord Lu searched everywhere for her

25:04.440 --> 25:05.440
but couldn't find her,

25:05.440 --> 25:07.370
so he joined the military instead.

25:07.550 --> 25:08.750
Only after he distinguished himself
in battle

25:08.750 --> 25:09.920
and became renowned across the land

25:09.920 --> 25:11.000
was Immortal Xin

25:11.000 --> 25:12.070
finally able to find him.

25:12.070 --> 25:13.130
So that's how it is…

25:13.480 --> 25:15.000
I had no idea
there was such a tragic backstory.

25:15.000 --> 25:16.480
How unfortunate.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.930
And the tragedy doesn't end there.

25:19.110 --> 25:20.240
After they

25:20.550 --> 25:22.480
finally reunited and got married—

25:22.880 --> 25:24.880
just when life was about
to turn for the better—

25:24.880 --> 25:25.810
they were framed

25:26.030 --> 25:27.750
by corrupt officials.

25:28.000 --> 25:29.160
While Immortal Xin was away,

25:29.160 --> 25:30.790
they took the opportunity to kill Lord Lu.

25:30.790 --> 25:32.030
Given how deeply they loved each other,

25:32.030 --> 25:33.290
how could Immortal Xin

25:33.440 --> 25:35.300
possibly let them go unpunished?

25:35.640 --> 25:38.100
A devoted couple,
bound by unwavering love.

25:38.590 --> 25:40.520
You two even have a story like that?

25:41.270 --> 25:42.160
Nonsense.

25:42.550 --> 25:43.960
You're the only one
who enjoys hearing this.

25:43.960 --> 25:44.440
Wrong—

25:44.880 --> 25:46.410
I enjoy all romantic tales.

25:46.480 --> 25:47.880
to all romantic affairs.

25:50.880 --> 25:51.750
So she really thinks

25:51.750 --> 25:53.750
she's some peerless wandering hero,

25:53.750 --> 25:55.480
capable of standing up for injustice

25:55.480 --> 25:56.280
in this world.

25:57.550 --> 25:58.550
That Mr. Gui—

25:58.750 --> 25:59.750
I've heard of him—

26:00.110 --> 26:01.710
he seems to be from Beixiang,

26:02.000 --> 26:03.200
a heretical cultivator

26:03.200 --> 26:05.000
who specializes in sinister
and deceitful arts.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.790
Though he's currently only
at Qi Refining stage 9,

26:06.790 --> 26:07.770
he's just half a step away

26:07.770 --> 26:09.100
from breaking through.

26:09.680 --> 26:11.350
With Xin Mei's current techniques,

26:11.350 --> 26:12.640
escaping from him

26:13.160 --> 26:14.680
must have cost her dearly.

26:15.640 --> 26:17.310
One Mr. Gui is nothing to fear.

26:17.480 --> 26:18.880
If those cultivators who were
at the Safe Haven Inn that day

26:18.880 --> 26:20.480
had also arrived,

26:20.880 --> 26:23.210
then things would have been troublesome.

26:28.440 --> 26:30.210
Sachet pendants.

26:29.910 --> 26:32.710
[Pingxiang Town]

26:30.720 --> 26:31.590
Take a look!

26:32.030 --> 26:33.480
Sachets and trinkets for sale!

26:33.480 --> 26:34.640
Lianxin...

26:35.550 --> 26:37.240
Lianxin, wake up!

26:37.240 --> 26:38.110
Lianxin...

26:38.640 --> 26:40.480
My daughter has been poisoned
by snake venom

26:40.480 --> 26:41.110
and urgently needs

26:41.110 --> 26:43.350
a top-grade Ghost Needle Lotus
to detoxify her.

26:43.350 --> 26:44.790
Won't someone

26:44.790 --> 26:46.240
please save my daughter?

26:46.240 --> 26:47.350
Lianxin...

26:49.200 --> 26:50.310
We're not beggars—

26:50.310 --> 26:51.720
we don't want money.

26:51.720 --> 26:53.450
Is there anyone kind-hearted?

26:53.680 --> 26:54.400
Miss.

26:54.680 --> 26:55.480
Miss, please!

26:55.590 --> 26:57.400
Please save my daughter.

26:57.890 --> 26:58.800
The doctor said

26:58.830 --> 26:59.680
she only needs

26:59.680 --> 27:02.080
a top-grade Ghost Needle Lotus
to save her.

27:02.350 --> 27:04.210
Miss. Please, I beg you—save her!

27:05.070 --> 27:06.070
I beg you!

27:13.480 --> 27:14.140
Lianxin...

27:14.240 --> 27:14.840
Mother...

27:15.110 --> 27:15.840
She's awake!

27:16.350 --> 27:17.440
She's really awake!

27:17.440 --> 27:18.440
A miracle doctor…

27:19.110 --> 27:20.640
She's truly kind-hearted!

27:21.200 --> 27:22.160
She's getting better.

27:22.160 --> 27:23.560
Is this an immortal pill?

27:24.200 --> 27:25.330
Is she a cultivator?

27:26.110 --> 27:26.790
She must be.

27:27.640 --> 27:28.640
So powerful…

27:32.920 --> 27:33.680
Madam,

27:33.750 --> 27:35.610
you should go thank her properly.

28:45.000 --> 28:46.400
Why are you following me?

28:52.830 --> 28:54.230
Don't follow me anymore.

29:10.160 --> 29:11.090
Dishes are here!

29:12.310 --> 29:12.970
Here you go.

29:21.200 --> 29:22.730
Sir, are you not satisfied?

29:23.200 --> 29:23.720
No.

29:23.960 --> 29:25.020
Just give him wine—

29:25.160 --> 29:26.360
the dishes are for me.

29:26.550 --> 29:27.080
Alright.

29:32.030 --> 29:32.960
Enjoy your meal.

29:38.640 --> 29:40.030
Hot steamed buns!

29:40.480 --> 29:41.880
Fresh hot buns!

29:43.070 --> 29:43.920
Come on, sir.

29:44.240 --> 29:44.790
Come on.

29:45.070 --> 29:46.530
Would you like to have one?

29:47.270 --> 29:48.110
Buns!

29:48.510 --> 29:50.110
Fresh hot buns!

29:57.350 --> 29:58.010
Come again.

30:04.110 --> 30:05.440
What are you looking at?

30:06.640 --> 30:07.240
Nothing.

30:08.350 --> 30:09.750
Must've been my mistake.

30:10.270 --> 30:11.960
Jin Lun should be arriving soon, right?

30:11.960 --> 30:12.830
Not necessarily.

30:12.830 --> 30:13.400
He came in response

30:13.400 --> 30:14.750
to a letter from Tianyin Mountain,

30:14.750 --> 30:16.070
but I don't think

30:16.070 --> 30:17.310
he's very interested in this matter.

30:17.310 --> 30:19.510
He probably won't arrive anytime soon.

30:19.590 --> 30:20.190
Forget it.

30:20.400 --> 30:21.720
Let's not worry about him for now—

30:21.720 --> 30:23.650
the important matters come first.

30:25.110 --> 30:27.200
The people from the immortal sects
have arrived.

30:27.200 --> 30:28.920
She's now caught
in the center of the storm.

30:28.920 --> 30:30.450
If we don't find her quickly

30:30.550 --> 30:32.070
and someone gets there first,

30:32.070 --> 30:33.310
she could be in danger.

30:33.310 --> 30:34.110
Someone got her first?

30:34.110 --> 30:35.310
Just take her back then.

30:35.310 --> 30:36.910
Who could possibly beat you?

30:37.510 --> 30:39.110
Can you keep a lower profile?

30:39.790 --> 30:41.480
Well, she is your wife after all.

30:41.480 --> 30:42.200
How did I

30:42.200 --> 30:43.000
not notice before?

30:43.000 --> 30:43.530
She looks

30:43.640 --> 30:44.920
so quiet and proper,

30:45.240 --> 30:46.900
yet she actually did all this.

31:36.750 --> 31:38.510
Is Xin still not awake?

31:39.240 --> 31:40.790
Why is she still bleeding?

31:41.160 --> 31:43.030
Is she going to die?

31:43.550 --> 31:44.750
Don't talk nonsense.

31:44.750 --> 31:46.400
Xin is an immortal—

31:46.480 --> 31:47.960
she has divine powers and can fly.

31:47.960 --> 31:49.770
You saw it yourself, didn't you?

31:50.920 --> 31:53.120
But does that mean immortals can't die?

31:53.720 --> 31:54.880
People say

31:55.310 --> 31:57.550
the world has become like this

31:57.830 --> 32:00.880
precisely because the gods
have all died off.

32:01.830 --> 32:03.240
If Xin dies,

32:03.680 --> 32:05.550
even Father in the underworld

32:05.720 --> 32:08.110
will blame us.

32:09.310 --> 32:11.440
Maybe we should

32:11.440 --> 32:12.960
find a doctor for her?

32:13.070 --> 32:14.480
We don't have any money.

32:21.110 --> 32:23.270
Then sell me

32:23.750 --> 32:24.960
for silver

32:25.200 --> 32:27.350
and use it to hire a doctor for Xin.

32:27.400 --> 32:28.800
How much can you sell for?

32:29.200 --> 32:31.530
It wouldn't even be enough
to pay a doctor.

32:33.920 --> 32:36.000
If only Father were still here…

32:36.550 --> 32:37.790
He was so capable.

32:38.350 --> 32:40.920
He would definitely have a way
to save Xin.

32:41.030 --> 32:42.200
If Father were here,

32:43.440 --> 32:45.720
Xin wouldn't have had to come
to the capital either.

32:45.720 --> 32:47.350
Ten-Complete Tonic Pill!

32:47.640 --> 32:48.970
It cures all illnesses!

32:49.110 --> 32:51.110
Instant relief!

32:53.680 --> 32:55.070
-Ten-Complete...
-Doctor!

32:55.070 --> 32:56.470
Can you treat illnesses?

32:57.590 --> 32:59.250
What kind of question is that?

32:59.510 --> 33:02.000
If I can't treat illnesses,
can I still be called a doctor?

33:02.000 --> 33:03.110
See this box?

33:03.440 --> 33:05.110
Inside are my spirit pills,

33:05.480 --> 33:07.790
the "Ten-Complete Tonic Pill,"

33:08.030 --> 33:09.640
refined from ten kinds

33:09.640 --> 33:11.350
of heavenly materials
and earthly treasures.

33:11.350 --> 33:12.680
They can cure all diseases.

33:12.680 --> 33:14.240
But let's make this clear first—

33:14.240 --> 33:15.920
my price is not low.

33:16.200 --> 33:17.070
No problem.

33:17.480 --> 33:18.270
Come with me.

33:19.310 --> 33:19.840
Alright,

33:20.110 --> 33:20.640
let's go.

33:27.770 --> 33:29.680
We know your consultation fee
is very high,

33:29.680 --> 33:31.480
but we don't have any money right now.

33:31.480 --> 33:33.830
However, that lady over there
is an immortal.

33:33.830 --> 33:34.870
If you save her,

33:35.160 --> 33:36.620
she will surely repay you.

33:38.310 --> 33:39.790
When we grow up and earn money,

33:39.790 --> 33:41.050
we'll pay you back too.

33:42.920 --> 33:44.250
-Help!
-Stop shouting.

33:46.270 --> 33:48.330
It's not that I don't want to save her—

33:48.920 --> 33:51.200
I simply can't.

33:51.510 --> 33:54.240
I'm just a quack
selling fake medicine for money.

33:57.460 --> 34:02.250
[Liang Residence]

34:03.720 --> 34:04.320
Well then,

34:04.680 --> 34:07.310
it is our honor that you both have come.

34:07.680 --> 34:09.670
This time we must capture
that enchantress

34:09.670 --> 34:11.070
and properly punish her.

34:11.510 --> 34:12.110
My Lord,

34:12.440 --> 34:13.969
what you should be doing now

34:14.230 --> 34:15.840
is bathing, burning incense,

34:15.840 --> 34:17.110
loosening your body,

34:17.280 --> 34:18.610
and getting a good rest.

34:18.800 --> 34:20.150
It is because when you wake up,

34:20.150 --> 34:22.000
that enchantress will already be bound

34:22.000 --> 34:22.730
in this hall.

34:23.110 --> 34:23.550
For...

34:24.110 --> 34:24.639
for real?

34:24.760 --> 34:26.230
Even if you don't trust me,

34:26.550 --> 34:27.360
surely you can

34:27.590 --> 34:29.440
trust Lingji Mountain, can't you?

34:29.440 --> 34:31.320
I am the young sect master
of Lingji Mountain—

34:31.320 --> 34:32.400
Lin An is my father.

34:33.030 --> 34:34.320
I've come in person myself,

34:34.320 --> 34:36.449
so what is there for you to worry about?

34:37.800 --> 34:38.190
Then…

34:38.400 --> 34:41.130
we'll have to trouble you two,
immortal masters.

34:54.550 --> 34:56.210
Why do I smell something sour?

34:57.880 --> 34:59.440
Sour jujube calms the spirit,

34:59.440 --> 35:00.970
and lily soothes the heart—

35:01.030 --> 35:02.110
both help with sleep

35:02.110 --> 35:03.970
and protect against nightmares.

35:05.150 --> 35:06.280
Looks like that lord

35:06.590 --> 35:08.190
was truly quite frightened.

35:09.960 --> 35:10.840
By the way,

35:11.150 --> 35:13.230
why haven't Jin Lun and Nangong Guhong

35:13.230 --> 35:14.070
arrived yet?

35:15.400 --> 35:16.070
Forget it.

35:16.840 --> 35:18.370
Let's not bother with them.

35:18.510 --> 35:20.030
The capital spans over a hundred li.

35:20.030 --> 35:21.110
If that female cultivator

35:21.110 --> 35:23.440
continues to conceal her aura
and doesn't act again,

35:23.440 --> 35:25.300
where are we supposed to find her?

35:34.030 --> 35:35.030
And I don't know where

35:35.030 --> 35:35.960
Senior Bai went.

35:36.360 --> 35:37.820
Why hasn't he arrived yet?

35:39.880 --> 35:41.010
As for Bai Zongying,

35:41.280 --> 35:42.610
he does have some skill,

35:42.800 --> 35:45.200
but tracking people
is not his strong suit.

35:45.320 --> 35:46.250
Do you have a way?

35:47.070 --> 35:49.000
Mr. Gui is a Qi cultivator

35:49.480 --> 35:51.010
with little innate talent,

35:51.150 --> 35:53.280
but he managed to gain a reputation
in the immortal sects

35:53.280 --> 35:55.950
entirely through his spiritual artifact,
the Sunblock Banner.

35:55.950 --> 35:57.540
Leaving aside how much

35:57.630 --> 35:59.360
spiritual energy this banner contains,

35:59.360 --> 36:00.960
the most important thing is—

36:00.960 --> 36:03.230
it is alive.

36:04.590 --> 36:05.230
Alive?

36:06.360 --> 36:07.420
Yes, that's right.

36:07.590 --> 36:09.710
It has already become an artifact spirit.

36:09.710 --> 36:11.070
Though it cannot take form

36:11.070 --> 36:12.230
or speak,

36:12.590 --> 36:13.390
it has already

36:13.630 --> 36:14.890
developed sentience.

36:15.190 --> 36:16.480
It must parasitize

36:16.590 --> 36:17.840
living flesh

36:17.960 --> 36:18.960
to survive,

36:19.550 --> 36:20.440
which is why Mr. Gui

36:20.440 --> 36:21.150
fed it

36:21.150 --> 36:22.950
his own essence blood every day.

36:22.960 --> 36:24.490
But now that Mr. Gui is dead,

36:24.800 --> 36:26.460
its whereabouts are unknown.

36:27.140 --> 36:28.800
Where do you think such a thing

36:29.000 --> 36:30.480
could have gone?

36:51.710 --> 36:54.040
This Sunblock Banner
is an evil artifact.

36:54.800 --> 36:56.510
I've heard it was refined

36:56.510 --> 36:58.230
only after absorbing

36:58.280 --> 36:59.630
the essence blood of 49 people—

36:59.630 --> 37:02.360
making it an object
of extreme darkness and yin energy.

37:02.360 --> 37:03.800
Wherever it is,

37:04.320 --> 37:06.050
not a trace of light can appear.

37:07.320 --> 37:07.960
So

37:08.400 --> 37:09.480
wherever it is,

37:09.880 --> 37:11.210
even lamps can't be lit.

37:12.550 --> 37:13.680
Jiang Ji, you really

37:13.710 --> 37:15.230
are quite perceptive.

37:28.800 --> 37:29.550
Strange…

37:30.360 --> 37:31.620
there's no wind at all.

37:33.150 --> 37:34.680
Jiujiu, where's the flint?

37:37.280 --> 37:38.210
Take it with you.

37:44.470 --> 37:46.000
Why won't it strike a spark?

37:46.230 --> 37:48.090
It was working just fine earlier.

37:49.400 --> 37:50.730
That is indeed a method.

37:51.510 --> 37:53.920
However, the capital spans
over a hundred li—

37:53.920 --> 37:55.080
if we were to light lamps everywhere,

37:55.080 --> 37:57.110
it would consume a tremendous amount
of spiritual power.

37:57.110 --> 37:58.800
I've brought the Yangyuan Pills with me—

37:58.800 --> 38:00.110
leave this small matter

38:00.110 --> 38:00.960
to me.

38:01.630 --> 38:02.360
Jiang Ji, you just need

38:02.360 --> 38:03.360
to find a high vantage point

38:03.360 --> 38:04.020
in the city,

38:04.330 --> 38:05.290
preferably one

38:05.320 --> 38:07.320
that overlooks the entire capital.

38:07.360 --> 38:08.070
Once I

38:08.190 --> 38:09.450
activate my formation

38:09.550 --> 38:10.880
and light up all the lamps,

38:10.880 --> 38:12.320
the darkest place in the city

38:12.320 --> 38:14.850
will be where the Sunblock Banner
is located.

38:15.030 --> 38:15.560
Alright.

38:43.710 --> 38:45.240
The snow hasn't melted yet.

38:47.480 --> 38:48.190
Snow?

38:49.320 --> 38:51.000
Immortal Xin made it fall for you.

38:51.000 --> 38:52.230
Snow falling at this time…

38:52.230 --> 38:53.440
there must be a great injustice.

38:53.440 --> 38:55.700
She's doing this to seek justice for you.

39:12.770 --> 39:14.500
Have you found any trace of her?

39:14.710 --> 39:16.230
I didn't find Immortal Xin,

39:16.230 --> 39:18.230
but I did get something unexpected.

39:18.440 --> 39:20.360
Guess who I saw in the city?

39:21.550 --> 39:23.400
Those cultivators from the inn?

39:23.920 --> 39:25.120
Two more joined them.

39:25.480 --> 39:26.510
One with a flute,

39:26.710 --> 39:27.230
and that

39:27.230 --> 39:29.110
little enchantress who teased you.

39:29.110 --> 39:30.040
But don't worry,

39:30.400 --> 39:31.600
even my flock of birds

39:31.630 --> 39:33.070
couldn't find Immortal Xin—

39:33.070 --> 39:35.190
neither can they.

40:15.880 --> 40:17.590
Primordial spirit, stabilize the soul.

40:17.590 --> 40:19.720
A thousand lanterns, guided by blood.

40:20.000 --> 40:20.510
Rise.

40:36.920 --> 40:37.850
What's going on?

40:38.150 --> 40:39.680
My Lord, I'll go take a look.

40:44.590 --> 40:45.440
My Lord, there's no need to worry—

40:45.440 --> 40:46.920
it seems the immortal masters
are casting a spell.

40:46.920 --> 40:47.670
Good, good.

40:58.400 --> 40:58.960
Easy now—

41:00.150 --> 41:01.880
it'll be your turn soon enough.

41:09.110 --> 41:10.370
Immortal techniques…

41:10.800 --> 41:12.260
What are they trying to do?

41:12.760 --> 41:13.320
No idea.

41:14.150 --> 41:15.210
But whatever it is,

41:15.550 --> 41:16.420
it can't be good for Xin Mei.
